    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it\u2014it\u2019s honestly in showroom condition and looks like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out without a single scratch in sight. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that 'new car' feel. I'm so excited for whoever gets to take this home and enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
