      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six power plant with its signature individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically flawless, having undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite including a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul, prophylactic replacement of rod bearings with VAC Motorsports coated shells, and a structural reinforcement of the rear subframe. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise gate engagement, paired with a refreshed Sachs clutch and a limited-slip variable M differential lock. The suspension maintains its factory-spec kinematics with fresh bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. Finished in Laguna Seca Blue with exceptional paint depth and zero orange peel correction needed, the cabin remains pristine with no leather bolster fatigue or dead pixels in the instrument cluster. A truly turn-key, analog masterpiece for the serious collector.",
